<div class="w-full mx-auto px-6 md:px-12 xl:px-6 bg-black">
  <div class="relative pb-10 pt-10 sm:pt-10 sm:pb-10 ml-auto min-h-full flex flex-col items-center">
    <h1 class="font-header text-white font-semibold text-3xl md:text-4xl xl:text-5xl mt-12 mb-4">FAQ</h1>
    <h3 class="text-white font-header text-lg md:text-xl xl:text-2xl mb-2">What is a Hackathon?</h3>
    <p class="text-gray-100 text-sm md:text-lg xl:text-xl mb-6 max-w-lg"> 
      A hackathon is an event at which programmers of all skill levels can come together and create. They are perfect opportunities to experiment and learn.
    </p>
    <h3 class="text-white font-header text-lg md:text-xl xl:text-2xl mb-2">Who can attend? Is it free?</h3>
    <p class="text-gray-100 text-sm md:text-lg xl:text-xl mb-6 max-w-lg">
      Anyone currently in high school or 8th grade. Yes! Admission, swag, workshops -- everything is free.
    </p>
    <h3 class="text-white font-header text-lg md:text-xl xl:text-2xl mb-2">Do I need a team?</h3>
    <p class="text-gray-100 text-sm md:text-lg xl:text-xl mb-6 max-w-lg">
      No, but we strongly encourage collaboration, so if you don’t have a team, let us know on the RSVP form and we’ll help you find one.
    </p>
    <h3 class="text-white font-header text-lg md:text-xl xl:text-2xl mb-2">What should I bring? Do I need experience?</h3>
    <p class="text-gray-100 text-sm md:text-lg xl:text-xl mb-6 max-w-lg">
      A laptop, a charger, and yourself! No prior experience is needed! We can provide laptops if needed.
    </p>
    <h3 class="text-white font-header text-lg md:text-xl xl:text-2xl mb-2">Do I have to stay for the whole event?</h3>
    <p class="text-gray-100 text-sm md:text-lg xl:text-xl mb-6 max-w-lg">
      No. We understand that everyone has busy schedules and may not be able to stay for the entire event. Contact us to make arrangements.
    </p>
